Source: libcio
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Warren MacEvoy <wmacevoy@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), libutf8-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://github.com/wmacevoy/cio

Package: libcio-1
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lightweight abstract character I/O library for C
 Provides a polymorphic I/O interface with pluggable backends
 including arrays, FILE streams, and UTF-8 codec layers.
 Uses function-pointer dispatch for read/write/peek/close operations.

Package: libcio-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libcio-1 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lightweight abstract character I/O library for C (development files)
 Provides a polymorphic I/O interface with pluggable backends
 including arrays, FILE streams, and UTF-8 codec layers.
 Uses function-pointer dispatch for read/write/peek/close operations.
 .
 This package contains the header files and static library for development.
